data.description: Central location, low maintenance, great floor plan....this is the perfect home for a family on the go! Located in popular Palmetto Trace, you're just minutes from Pier Park, schools, golf courses and you can walk to Frank Brown Park. There's a community pool just a out the back door, but you don't have to worry with the day to day maintenance of a pool. Lawn care, pine straw and twice annual building pressure washing  is also taken care of by the Homeowners Association so that leaves more time to go play catch with the kids. Inside the home, you'll find a large master bedroom on the main level with walk -in closet.  There are two bedrooms with a ''Jack-n-Jill'' bathroom on the second level as well as a loft area perfect for home office, children's play area, or a small home theater.
